text: Marmylevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Zhukovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 232 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Ufa, 10 km from Zhukovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Marmylevo
